@node HISTORY

   Revision V1.6
   --------------
     - backslash is repeatable now
     - added all missing keycodes (keypad codes, tilde etc.)

   Revision V1.5
   --------------
     - DYNAMOUSE tooltype was not handled correctly
     - added semaphore for MouseServ
     - added support for new mouseserv

   Revision V1.4
   --------------
     - again changed keyboard emulation code.
     - fixed some enforcer hits in the HandleGUI code

   Revision V1.3
   --------------
     - changed the way the keyboard is emulated.
     - the '4'-key works now
     - the backslash is emulated correctly now
     - output to file is now enabled

   Revision V1.2 (first public release)
   ------------------------------------
     - added menu with about/quit function
       added hotkey to toggle lpt activate function
     - added lpt support. File output not implemented yet.
  
   Revision V1.1
   --------------
     - added user interface
  
   Revision V1.0
   --------------
       --- Initial release ---

@endnode
